<subSubSection pageId="254" pageNumber="255" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="254.[151,1437,895,1424]" pageId="254" pageNumber="255">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1364,1388]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="254" pageNumber="255" reason="1">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species is included in the key to intertidal pinnotherids of central 
<collectingRegion box="[1142,1256,1364,1388]" country="United States of America" name="California" pageId="254" pageNumber="255">California</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingRegion box="[1314,1398,1364,1388]" country="United States of America" name="Oregon" pageId="254" pageNumber="255">Oregon</collectingRegion>
by Campos (2007), but there are no records of the crab north of Point Arguello.
</paragraph>
